import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
sns.set(font="Droid Sans",font_scale = 2)
sns.set_style("whitegrid")
sns.set_color_codes("dark")

data = pd.read_csv('evaluation_data.csv')

sparkData = data[data['model'] == 'spark']
flinkData = data[data['model'] == 'flink']

_ =plt.subplots(2,2,figsize=(15,15))
_ =plt.subplot(2,2,1)
maxHit = flinkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['hit'].max().rename(columns={'hit':'max'})
_ =plt.plot(maxHit['numIter'], maxHit['max'], '-o', label='flink', color='red')
maxHit = sparkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['hit'].max().rename(columns={'hit':'max'})
_ =plt.plot(maxHit['numIter'], maxHit['max'], '-o', label='spark')

_ =plt.legend(loc='lower right')
_ =plt.title('Hits')
_ =plt.xlabel('numIter')
_ =plt.ylabel('hits')
_ =plt.xlim(1,8)

_ =plt.subplot(2,2,2)
maxnDCG = flinkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['nDCG@10'].max().rename(columns={'nDCG@10':'max'})
_ =plt.plot(maxnDCG['numIter'], maxnDCG['max'], '-o', label='flink', color='red')
maxnDCG = sparkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['nDCG@10'].max().rename(columns={'nDCG@10':'max'})
_ =plt.plot(maxnDCG['numIter'], maxnDCG['max'], '-o', label='spark')

_ =plt.legend(loc='lower right')
_ =plt.title('nDCG@10')
_ =plt.xlabel('numIter')
_ =plt.ylabel('nDCG@10')
_ =plt.xlim(1,8)

_ =plt.subplot(2,2,3)
maxPrec = flinkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['Prec@10'].max().rename(columns={'Prec@10':'max'})
_ =plt.plot(maxPrec['numIter'], maxPrec['max'], '-o', label='flink', color='red')
maxPrec = sparkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['Prec@10'].max().rename(columns={'Prec@10':'max'})
_ =plt.plot(maxPrec['numIter'], maxPrec['max'], '-o', label='spark')

_ =plt.legend(loc='lower right')
_ =plt.title('Prec@10')
_ =plt.xlabel('numIter')
_ =plt.ylabel('Prec@10')
_ =plt.xlim(1,8)

_ =plt.subplot(2,2,4)
maxRecall = flinkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['Recall@10'].max().rename(columns={'Recall@10':'max'})
_ =plt.plot(maxRecall['numIter'], maxRecall['max'], '-o', label='flink', color='red')
maxRecall = sparkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['Recall@10'].max().rename(columns={'Recall@10':'max'})
_ =plt.plot(maxRecall['numIter'], maxRecall['max'], '-o', label='spark')

_ =plt.legend(loc='lower right')
_ =plt.title('Recall@10')
_ =plt.xlabel('numIter')
_ =plt.ylabel('recall@10')
_ =plt.xlim(1,8)

_ =plt.tight_layout()

minTime = flinkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['learningTime'].min().rename(columns={'learningTime':'min'})
_ = plt.plot(minTime['numIter'], minTime['min'], '-o', label='flink', color='red')
minTime = sparkData.groupby('numIter', as_index=False)['learningTime'].max().rename(columns={'learningTime':'min'})
_ = plt.plot(minTime['numIter'], minTime['min'], '-o', label='spark')
_ = plt.legend(loc='upper right')
_ = plt.title('learningTime')
_ = plt.xlabel('numIter')
_ = plt.ylabel('learningTime in sec')
_ = plt.xlim(1,8)

_ = plt.tight_layout()
